(Z.Z. Zhou &amp; Z.W. Xie) Sima &amp; S.G. Lu. In: 
<bibRefCitation id="AA9FC7283DADA796F645200C23DEF6E6" author="Sima, YK" journalOrPublisher="PhD Thesis, Yunnan University, Kunming" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" publicationUrl="http://www.docin.com/p-1050989203.html" refId="B71" refString="Sima, YK, 2011. A Taxonomic Revision of the Magnoliaceae from China. PhD Thesis, Yunnan University, Kunming, http://www.docin.com/p-1050989203.html" title="A Taxonomic Revision of the Magnoliaceae from China." url="http://www.docin.com/p-1050989203.html" year="2011">Sima (2011</bibRefCitation>
: 163), p.p. quoad syn. 
<taxonomicName id="C82BBD89FD3833B3D794B07851404A51" authority="Spach, 1839" authorityName="Spach" authorityYear="1839" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Magnoliaceae" genus="Yulania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Yulania pilocarpa subsp. var. var. ellipticifolia" order="Magnoliales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="pilocarpa" subSpecies="var." variety="ellipticifolia">Yulania pilocarpa var. ellipticifolia</taxonomicName>
D.L. Fu et al.
